      "height": 130,
      "text": "extract_text(bytes, filename)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nRouting by file extension:\n\nв”њв”Ђ .txt  в†’  _extract_txt()\nв”‚          decode: UTF-8 в†’ latin-1 в†’ cp1252\nв”‚\nв”њв”Ђ .pdf  в†’  _extract_pdf()\nв”‚          PyPDF2.PdfReader\nв”‚          extract_text() per page\nв”‚\nв””в”Ђ .docx в†’  _extract_docx()\n           python-docx.Document\n           collect non-empty paragraphs\n\nRaises ValueError if unsupported.",
      "fontSize": 10,
