    {
      "id": "text-mcg-build-prompt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 675,
      "y": 478,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "build_user_prompt()\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n1. Wraps training material\n   inside user message\n\n2. If exclude_questions exists:\n   appends \"DO NOT REPEAT\"\n   block with all previous\n   Q + answer pairs\n\n3. SYSTEM_PROMPT defines\n   JSON schema + rules",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#0d47a1"
    },
    {
      "id": "text-mcg-generate",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": 478,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "generate_mcqs()\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n1. Validate api_key provided\n\n2. Create Anthropic client\n   (base_url: api.anthropic.com)\n\n3. Retry loop (max 3 attempts)\n\n4. For each attempt:\n   в†’ _call_api()\n   в†’ Try 3 JSON strategies\n   в†’ Pydantic validation\n\n5. On all fail в†’ raise ValueError",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#0d47a1"
    },
    {
      "id": "text-mcg-call-api",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 675,
      "y": 595,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "_call_api()\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nclient.messages.create(\n  model      = \"claude-haiku-4-5\",\n  max_tokens = 2048,\n  temperature = 0.8,\n  system     = SYSTEM_PROMPT,\n  messages   = [...]\n)\n\nReturns response.content[n].text",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#0d47a1"
    },
    {
      "id": "text-mcg-json",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": 595,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "JSON Extraction Strategies\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n1. raw               в†’ json.loads()\n2. strip_fences()    в†’ remove ```json ```\n3. scan_anywhere()   в†’ find first balanced\n                        { or [ in response\n\nEach strategy: json.loads() в†’\nMCQList.model_validate()",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#0d47a1"
    },
