    },
    {
      "id": "text-api-call",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "HTTPS POST  в†’  https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nRequest:\n  Authorization: Bearer <user API key from sidebar>\n  model:        claude-haiku-4-5 | claude-sonnet-4 | claude-opus-4\n  max_tokens:   2048\n  temperature:  0.8  (variety, not fully random)\n  system:        JSON schema + generation rules\n  messages:      [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": <user prompt + do-not-repeat block>}]\n\nResponse:\n  content: [TextBlock(text='<raw JSON>'), ...]\n  If parse/validation fails в†’ HTTP 200 but Python-side retry (up to 3Г—)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#4527a0"
    },
