      "width": 320,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "temperature = 0.8\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n0.0  в†’  Deterministic\n        Same input = same output\n0.3  в†’  Low variety, high accuracy\n0.8  в†’  RECOMMENDED: variety +\n        quality balance\n1.0  в†’  Max randomness, quality risk\n\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nModel Selection:\nв”њв”Ђ Haiku 4.5  в†’  Default, fast, cheap\nв”њв”Ђ Sonnet 4   в†’  Better reasoning\nв””в”Ђ Opus 4     в†’  Best quality, costly",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#2e7d32"
    },
    {
      "id": "box-dedup",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 1040,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "fillColor": "#fce4ec",
      "strokeColor": "#c62828",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "borderRadius": 10,
      "label": {
        "text": "Deep Dive: Deduplication",
        "fontSize": 13,
        "fontFamily": "Arial",
        "color": "#c62828",
        "bold": true,
        "textAlign": "center"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "text-dedup",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1510,
      "y": 1080,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "How repetition is prevented\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nClick 1: session_state.mcqs = []\n  в†’ API receives no exclusion list\n  в†’ Generates 5 questions Q1-Q5\n  в†’ Displayed + stored in mcqs\n\nClick 2: session_state.mcqs = [Q1-Q5]\n  в†’ Passed as exclude_questions\n  в†’ build_user_prompt() appends:\n    \"DO NOT REPEAT: Q1...Q5\"\n  в†’ Model forced to generate Q6-Q10\n\nClick N: same pattern repeats\n  в†’ All previous questions excluded\n  в†’ Exhausts unique topics naturally\n    (no more new questions possible)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#c62828"
    },
    {
      "id": "box-session-flow",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1500,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "fillColor": "#e3f2fd",
      "strokeColor": "#1565c0",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "borderRadius": 10,
      "label": {
        "text": "Deep Dive: Session State",
        "fontSize": 13,
        "fontFamily": "Arial",
        "color": "#1565c0",
        "bold": true,
        "textAlign": "center"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "text-session-flow",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1510,
      "y": 1340,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "st.session_state lifecycle\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n_init_state() runs once on import:\n  setdefault for all keys\n\nOn API key change в†’ st.rerun()\nOn model change   в†’ clear mcqs\nOn new upload     в†’ clear mcqs\nOn Generate click в†’ replace mcqs\n\nWhy not append?\n  SPEC requires: \"Each click\n  replaces (not appends)\"\n\nexclude_questions carries the\nhistory forward вЂ” decoupling\nUI behavior from API behavior.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": "Courier New",
      "color": "#0d47a1"
    },
